In the heat of battle, it's sometimes necessary to salvage enemy equipment, even wreckage, and recondition it to make it usable again, and why not use your own damaged ships to reassemble everything into something usable.


That's what's on offer here. The Magos of the Dark Mechanicum always take great pleasure in corrupting and reusing imperial technology so that they can use it against the imperium.
